#Just for FUN

``` css Setup grid values
@column_width: 45px;
@gutter: 10px;
@total_width: 980px;
```

``` css standard
.std(@x){
	width: ((@column_width)*@x)+(@gutter*((@x*-1)+1)*-1);
	float: left; 
	display: inline;
}
```

``` css column
.col(@x, @last:0) when (@last = 0 ) { 
	.std(@x); 
	margin-right: @gutter; }

.col(@x, @last:0) when (@last = 1 ){ 
	.std(@x); 
	margin-right: 0; }
```
